txt.en: Several Warg pack-leaders and goblin Warg-riders patrol beyond the Warg-warrens.

'Several Warg pack-leaders and goblin Warg-riders have been sighted among the Warg-warrens east of here. These creatures clearly guide the actions of the Wargs and must be dealt with... I find it strange that the Dunlendings tolerate the vile creatures.\n\n'The Warg-warrens lie to the east of here, and the pack-leaders and Warg-riders can be found near there. Go forth and slay the vile beasts... for Théodred and Théoden King!'
Warg pack-leaders and goblin Warg-riders can be found near the Warg-warrens, east of Garrun's camp.\n\nGarrun asked you to defeat the pack-leaders and Warg-riders among the Warg-warrens.
'With their leadership dispatched, perhaps the rest of the pack will disperse and return from whence they came.'
Garrun is at his camp, west of the Warg-warrens.\n\nYou should return to Garrun with tidings of your success.
Talk to Garrun in the Isendale
